        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks EM for essay ["Sopra un rara anomalia dell’osso malare", <hi rend="italic">Annu. Soc. Nat. Modena</hi> 7 (1873): 1–50]. CD agrees as far as he understands. Cannot see how new modifications could arise by atavism. "The more I study nature, the more I feel convinced that species generally change by extremely slight modifications."</p> 
        </abstract>
